data.description: Welcome to this great investment opportunity! This property is distressed but has a ton of potential and just needs some TLC. This townhome highlights 3 spacious bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, a sizable kitchen and living room space, a finished basement and a 2.5 car garage. Also, this property has a stunning top floor master bedroom! This house is a SHORT SALE and is priced competitively to sale quickly. SOLD AS IS. Schedule your private tour now!
